parameters:
\SE[45]This... I can't help but laugh...!! To receive a
confession in such a state of mind...!?

\SE[43]Even though I was trying so hard...! \!\SE[44]To be
defeated in a game of strategy... To be caught up in
schemes...! \.Even coming up with childish responses...!

\SE[39]Ahaha! It's impossible, I can't help but laugh at
this...!

\SE[15]Now, you know... Mama is turning bright red, you
know? \SE[15]She's curling up at the corner and spinning
around in circles.

\SE[63]If someone sees me like this...! \!\SE[61]They'll
want to spin around in circles too...!

\SE[37]So that's how it was.... \SE[56]Luna was actually
nervous too.... I wasn't the only one....

\SE[2]I think this might be the first time I've seen your
genuinely laughing face.
\SE[0]Hey, Laura? \SE[0]Are you glad you came here...?

\SE[56]...I'm a little frustrated, but... \!\SE[55]I'm glad
I came here...\.

\SE[23]Luna's fun things and difficult things....
\SE[18]There are probably things that I don't know about,
and other things as well. But, that is surely...

\SE[59]It means we can understand each other more...
\!\SE[55]It means we can become closer...

\SE[2]I'm sure Mama would be better off being with Laura.
\SE[3]I think that would be for the best, for good things to
happen.

\SE[4]No, that's impossible. \SE[2]I can't let that child be
left alone.

\SE[4]I love that child too. \!\SE[0]I've come to love both
Mama and Laura. \!\SE[2]So, I hope everyone can be happy...

\SE[3]If 'that child' monopolizes 'Mama', then 'Laura' won't
be able to be happy....\SE[2]I just thought that would be a
little undesirable...

\SE[2]This dream ends here... Beyond this, that child is
waiting. \!\SE[15]I want to see an ending where everyone can
be happy.

\SE[4]Hey, Laura. \SE[2]Before we go meet that child... Can
I ask you to make a little detour?

\SE[2]Because it's not my territory... I think I can only
show you a little... \SE[0]I want you to know a little about
that child too.

\SE[5]...I understand. Okay. \!\SE[0]I feel like I should
know too.
When we were little, Luna and... me...?
Um, um...? There's something I want to ask Luna...
Um...? Well... When we grow up...
Sure! I want to marry Laura too!

(Ah... This is from before Luna went to school... It's been
5 years already... The past...)

But Papa said that you can only get married if it's between
a man and a woman...

I heard from the traveling poet! In the country called
Yurishin, girls can marry each other now!
Is that so? Then it's okay! Yes! I will marry Laura!

(I see... I have to tell Luna right away! The poet told
me...)

Yay! So, which one of us will be the bride? Luna, which one
do you prefer?

Laura can choose! ...Ah! How about the taller one becomes
the bride and the smaller one becomes the wife?
Oh no...! What if I don't grow at all...?

(Did I... say something like that...? I didn't grow much
taller, so maybe I'm the smaller one.)

I... I have to go to the magic academy starting next year...
So I won't be able to come back for 5 years...

It's okay! I'll wait forever! I'll wait until Luna becomes
amazing and comes back!

Really...? If that much time passes... will you forget about
me? Will you not like me anymore?

(There's no way that would happen. Even now... I love you so
much...)

There's no way that would happen! I'll always love you! I'll
wait forever!
So please don't say things like that... Waaahhh!!

Ah... Don't cry, Laura... But thank you... I was a little
worried... I'm going now... Please wait for me, okay?
(I used to be a crybaby... Luna often comforted me...)
Yeah! Then, let's get married when you come back!

...I know! Luna, since you love reading books, I'll make a
bookmark that you can use over there!
(I wonder if Luna still remembers... the promise?)

(I'm a little scared... but more than that... I want to
meet... and talk...)
